Package: osp.snapshots
Type: Package
Title: Import and Manipulate Open Systems Pharmacology Project Snapshots
Version: 0.1.0.9030
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Felix", "MIL",
      email = "felix.mil@esqlabs.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a convenient R interface for working with PKSIM project 
    snapshots exported as JSON files. You provide the snapshot file, and 
    'osp.snapshots' handles the complex nested structure, allowing you to 
    easily import, navigate, modify, and export snapshot data. Building 
    blocks can be converted to data frames for integration with the 
    'ospsuite' R framework and broader R ecosystem.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://esqlabs.github.io/osp.snapshots/
